title: Thousands Of Supporters Chant Kendrick Lamar Lyrics At The Million Man March
text:
Thousands Of Supporters Chant Kendrick Lamar Lyrics At The Million Man March 
Published By: MTV - Today 
Thousands of marchers in the nation's capital chanted Kendrick Lamar's "Alright" as they organized in recognition of black social issues....
